k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ccv1665702760000.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ccv1665702760000.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ccv1665702760000.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ccv1665702760000\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__uxmlwriter_445160\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">UXMLWRITER is an internal Uniface component that enables you to generate XML documents\n      rather than having to code each character in the XML stream yourself.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__p_d136379e1_d136380e1_d136381e1\">The UXMLWRITER component operations enable you to construct an XML document. The operations must be called in a specific sequence. If an operation is called when this is not legal, its return value will be <code class=\"ph codeph\">–1</code> and no text will be added to the XML document by the operation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__p_d136382e1_d136383e1_d136384e1\">For example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DOCCOMMENT</span> can only be called immediately after a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTDOCUMENT</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ENDELEMENT</span> or another <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DOCCOMMENT</span> invocation. It cannot be called immediately after calling <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">CHARACTERS</span>. In such cases, the return value is <code class=\"ph codeph\">–1</code> and no text is added to the XML document. Otherwise, the return value is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> and the comment is added to the document.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__topic_d97152e1_d97153e1_d97154e1_d97155e1_d97156e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1139355e86\">Operations</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__p_d136388e1_d136389e1_d136390e1\"> For descriptions of the operations, see the following topics.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48242e1_d48243e1_d48244e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zbn1665703203826.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbn1665703203826.html\" title=\"Retrieves a maximum of 10240000 characters of the XML stream generated thus far. This call can be repeated to obtain larger documents.\">GETDOCUMENT</a>—retrieves a\n               maximum of 10 MB of the XML stream generated thus far. This call can be repeated to\n               obtain larger documents. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48245e1_d48246e1_d48247e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myh1665702758943.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myh1665702758943.html\" title=\"Generates the beginning of the document, optionally with the XML version header.\">STARTDOCUMENT</a>—generates the\n               beginning of the document, optionally with the XML version header. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48248e1_d48249e1_d48250e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kpe1665702759011.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kpe1665702759011.html\" title=\"End the XML document, closing all open tags.\">ENDDOCUMENT</a> —ends the XML\n               document, closing all open tags. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48251e1_d48252e1_d48253e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvg1665702759219.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvg1665702759219.html\" title=\"Starts a new element using the name, including optional prefix and URI elements.\">STARTELEMENT</a>—starts a new\n               element using the name, including optional prefix and URI elements. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48254e1_d48255e1_d48256e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdp1665702759283.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdp1665702759283.html\" title=\"Ends an XML element by adding the closing tag.\">ENDELEMENT</a>—ends an XML\n               element by adding the closing tag. </li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rqe1665703206044.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rqe1665703206044.html\" title=\"Adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag.\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING</a>—adds a namespace to the beginning of an element\n               tag. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48257e1_d48258e1_d48259e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"trj1665703206355.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/trj1665703206355.html\" title=\"Adds an attribute to a start element tag.\">ADDATTRIBUTE</a>—adds an\n               attribute to a start element tag.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48260e1_d48261e1_d48262e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bry1665702759353.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bry1665702759353.html\" title=\"Adds the supplied text inside an element.\">CHARACTERS</a>—adds the\n               supplied text inside an element.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48263e1_d48264e1_d48265e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddv1665703206737.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddv1665703206737.html\" title=\"Inserts a &lt;![CDATA[ prefix and adds the unparsed content, as-is, to the XML document.\">CDATA</a>—adds a\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;![CDATA[</code> prefix and the unparsed content, as-is, to the XML\n               document. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccv1665702760000__li_d48266e1_d48267e1_d48268e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fwp1665703206975.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fwp1665703206975.html\" title=\"Adds an XML comment.\">DOCCOMMENT</a>—adds an XML\n               comment. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wzs1665702760065.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Generating Customized XML</a><p>To generate XML data, you can use the operations available from the UXMLWRITER component API.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526385\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526385\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UXMLWRITER Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 UXMLWRITER is an internal Uniface component that enables you to generate XML documents rather than having to code each character in the XML stream yourself. The UXMLWRITER component operations enable you to construct an XML document. The operations must be called in a specific sequence. If an operation is called when this is not legal, its return value will be –1 and no text will be added to the XML document by the operation. For example, DOCCOMMENT can only be called immediately after a STARTDOCUMENT , ENDELEMENT or another DOCCOMMENT invocation. It cannot be called immediately after calling STARTELEMENT or CHARACTERS . In such cases, the return value is –1 and no text is added to the XML document. Otherwise, the return value is 0 and the comment is added to the document. Operations For descriptions of the operations, see the following topics. GETDOCUMENT —retrieves a maximum of 10 MB of the XML stream generated thus far. This call can be repeated to obtain larger documents. STARTDOCUMENT —generates the beginning of the document, optionally with the XML version header. ENDDOCUMENT —ends the XML document, closing all open tags. STARTELEMENT —starts a new element using the name, including optional prefix and URI elements. ENDELEMENT —ends an XML element by adding the closing tag. ADDPREFIXMAPPING —adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag. ADDATTRIBUTE —adds an attribute to a start element tag. CHARACTERS —adds the supplied text inside an element. CDATA —adds a <![CDATA[ prefix and the unparsed content, as-is, to the XML document. DOCCOMMENT —adds an XML comment. Related Links Generating Customized XML To generate XML data, you can use the operations available from the UXMLWRITER component API. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}